@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Cover Letter";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cover Letter - Eric Grigor</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        .main-container {
            margin: 2rem auto;
            max-width: 800px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="main-container">
    <p>[Today's Date]</p>
    <p>[Hiring Manager's Name]</p>
    <p>[Company Name]</p>
    <p>[Company Address]</p>
    <p>[City, State, Zip Code]</p>
    <br>
    <p>Dear [Hiring Manager's Name],</p>
    <br>
    <p>I am writing to express my interest in the C# ASP.Net MVC position at [Company Name]. As a professional with a background in hospitality and tourism, and a strong interest in Information Technology, I am excited about the opportunity to apply my skills in a new field. My customer service experience, along with my recent technical education, makes me an ideal candidate for this role.</p>

    <p>During my studies at George Brown College, I have gained extensive knowledge in various programming languages such as Python, Java, and C#. I have also developed full-stack web applications using ASP.NET Core and have experience with database management using SQL and Oracle Database. In addition, I am well-versed in various operating systems, web applications, and mobile technologies.</p>

    <p>My background in hospitality has enabled me to develop strong customer service and problem-solving skills, which I believe are valuable in any industry, including IT. I am confident in my ability to adapt to different working environments and conditions, ensuring that I can excel in diverse situations.</p>

    <p>I am excited about the prospect of contributing my skills and experiences to [Company Name] and would be delighted to discuss further how I can be an asset to your team. Thank you for considering my application, and I look forward to the opportunity to speak with you.</p>

    <br>
    <p>Sincerely,</p>
    <p>Eric Grigor</p>
</div
</body>
</html>
